RNAi Phenotypes

Source: R/rnaiPhenotypes.R
rnaiPhenotypes.Rd

RNAi Phenotypes

rnaiPhenotypes(version = NULL, dir = ".")

Arguments

version

WormBase version. If NULL, defaults to current production release version available on the WormBase website. Legacy versions can be specified as a string (e.g. "WS262").
dir

Output directory.

Value

tbl_df.

Examples

invisible(capture.output(
    x <- rnaiPhenotypes()
))
